name: Jules Against the World
description: Jules is about the freak out. She have to look after eleven cats, one rabbit, one freaky elf, and one fish... The kitchen was floaded a long time ago and she just say "f*ck it" and she bought a duckboat for rabbit-he just love kitchen and he doesnt want to go anywhere except kitchen-. And the train keeps louding all the time. She wears the angel costume for luck. But it didnt work actually... Just keep pushing and pushing all the time. Everybody in this house love her but they need food, drink, interest etc. She have to reach all of it. Btw the coffee on the table is made 4 or 5 years ago as u see the coffeecup is dead af. When the time comes Jules thinks that drinking it for her suicide haha. May god help her...
